post.description:
iOS ChatStreamService → chat-api POST /chat/stream (SSE).

Uses `_proxy_stream` so chunks reach iOS as the LLM produces them;
the standard buffered proxy would defeat SSE.

delete.description:
iOS "Remove device" → mapper-api DELETE /mobile/pairing/devices/{id}
(AMA-2029). Deletes the pairing token row — the watch must re-pair to
reconnect. `device_id` is the PairedDevice.id from GET /v1/devices.
